  • Packages that use StatisticMetricEx 
    Package Description
    com.genesyslab.platform.reporting.protocol.statserver
    This package contains objects that correspond to objects in the Genesys Configuration Layer, such as AgentStatus and PlaceGroup.
    com.genesyslab.platform.reporting.protocol.statserver.requests
    This package contains the Request objects that your applications can use to open, look at, and close statistics.
